title: Hopi Prophecy - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 11/4/20

description:
George Noory and researcher Bill Warwick explore his encounters with one of the few remaining elders of the Hopi Indian tribe, how they passed along stories of major events in world history, and if encounters with strange beings could be aliens or underground Earth dwellers.
